description: GOUT FUN — The Meme Launchpad built on GOUT Chain, GOUT FUN is a next-gen meme launchpad for seamless meme launches and trading. Its innovative Three-Pool Burn & Backstop Mechanism—spanning a liquidity pool, backstop pool, and rewards pool—drives sustained value capture and price stability for every meme project on the platform. GOUT FUN is a one-stop token launch and trading platform built on Binance Smart Chain and Goutchain. Through the innovative "triple-pool burn mechanism," we provide users with a simple and secure token issuance experience while continuously empowering project value and providing price protection
